c: 9
v: 127
t: "“Ndipo nthawi iliyonse sura yatsopano ikavumbulutsidwa amayang’anana (iwo achiphamaso kuti athawe, asamvere mawu ake, uku akuuzana pakati pawo): “Kodi alipo amene akukuonani?” Kenako amatembenuka nkuthawa. Tero, Allah waikhotetsa mitima yawo chifukwa chakuti iwo ndi anthu osazindikira"